metadata.name: Kiwi Fae
metadata.description:
Kiwi fae lives in a multi colored night sky of shipibo patterns and city lights


Chain Faeries:
A juxtaposition of a light hearted being weighed down by heavy yet ethereal chain 
Sometimes we don't want to be free
Sometimes the chains that hold us down are simply a costume to be worn .
Sometimes our scars and burdens can be beautiful too. 

Model & Digital Art : Flexible Serpent 
Photographer : Embodied Design Studio
